{"tid":635944,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"貶值的香港車牌","createTime":"2018-04-20T12:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T00:48:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"54ff43229598b01d48def7cd16b8112ebb2ba886","tid":635944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T12:26:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180420/20366714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F20366714&d=u4vMZptKPzrsiD3c04Gvk57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=833b5dac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180420%2F20366714&h=076cc4f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20180420/20366714</a><br />\n<br />\n貶值的香港車牌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180420/large/1524126455_eb54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180420%2Flarge%2F1524126455_eb54.jpg&h=a3b694c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n截至去年年底，一共有26萬7476名中國司機免試用中國車牌換取香港車牌，僅去年一年就有接近36000名。香港與中國的道路規則不同，駕駛方向相反，中國司機的駕駛態度更一向被人詬病，再加上中國崇尚「假貨比真貨好」的文化，車牌真假及獲取車牌的途徑莫測高深，香港運輸署輕率發牌，不但令本港道路安全增添不安全因素，同時也令本身有一定公信力的香港車牌在國際上貶值。<br />\n上運輸署網站搜索，原來中國車牌換領香港車牌幾乎不需要任何條件，如此大規模發牌，而又不設任何條件，不免讓人質疑這一做法背後的動機。<br />\n<br />\n任何國家都有外國車牌換領服務，但不是像香港這樣無條件換領的，除非對對方國家的車牌考試嚴謹程度投信任票。比如加拿大，香港車牌不能直接換領加拿大車牌，只能免去筆試，但仍須進行路試。<br />\n<br />\n至於澳洲和日本，擁有香港車牌超過一定年限的司機雖然可以免試換領，但是卻必須向當地運輸署提供許多證明文件，日本是居住超過三個月的證明文件，澳洲則須提供當地銀行發出的信用咭、四份當地住址證明（其中一份必須是銀行提供），這些條件是用來確證發當地車牌的必要性。限制濫發，以確保當地道路安全。<br />\n<br />\n香港運輸署不設條件把數十萬張本港車牌發給中國居民，究竟有甚麼必要？  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk <br />\n網頁：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkowaiyin.yoyoko&d=u4vMZptKPzrsiD3c04Gvk57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=50f6d291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/kowaiyin.yoyoko</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n出了一口冤氣 (蔣芸)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n習近平的惆悵 (古德明)"},{"pid":"0d0d5a56093aaf095611146164b37416d2bb4fc6","tid":635944,"uid":55632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"on9,香港車牌換日本一樣要考試！不過比普通隔單D，筆試都簡單D！<br />\n我之前有個係香港做司機，過到黎日本都一樣要考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係香港有牌，係日本考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790db065864c55340e8233c7f5f884a1dfbe73f7","tid":635944,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d0d5a56093aaf095611146164b37416d2bb4fc6","tid":635944,"uid":55632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"on9,香港車牌換日本一樣要考試！不過比普通隔單D，筆試都簡單D！<br />\n我之前有個係香港做司機，過到黎日本都一樣要考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己都係香港有牌，係日本考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:58:01.000Z","msg":"國際牌去日本咪變左無用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a630eed5c07e562f141ec1cfd689f04cab7df6","tid":635944,"uid":55632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"790db065864c55340e8233c7f5f884a1dfbe73f7","tid":635944,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d0d5a56093aaf095611146164b37416d2bb4fc6","tid":635944,"uid":55632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T11:56:16.000Z","msg":"o